---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Stedet — Thorbjørn & Lorena">
  <div class="venue">
    <h1 class="venue-name">Finca Prados Riveros</h1>

    <p class="description">
      Beliggende i Sierra de Guadarrama Nationalpark, en times kørsel nord for Madrid,
      er Finca Prados Riveros en 12 hektar stor familieejendom omgivet af skotske
      fyrreskovsområder og hundredårige egeskovsenge med panoramaudsigt over Peñalara.
      Det renoverede landhus, dets glasdrivhus og private hytter befinder sig midt i
      naturen, fuldt udstyret til en uforglemmelig fejring.
    </p>

    <div class="details">
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Adresse</span>
        <span class="detail-value">Camino del Palero, 11, 28740 Rascafría, Madrid, Spanien</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Hjemmeside</span>
        <a href="https://espaciospradosriveros.com" class="venue-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          espaciospradosriveros.com
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="getting-there-note">
      Fincaen ligger i en nationalpark — der er ingen offentlig transport til stedet.
      Vi arrangerer shuttlebusser fra Rascafría til alle gæster. Flere detaljer på
      <a href="/da/accommodation">Overnatning</a>-siden.
    </p>

    <iframe
      src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Finca+Prados+Riveros+%28Casa+El+Palero%29&output=embed"
      class="map-frame"
      loading="lazy"
      allowfullscreen
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
      title="Finca Prados Riveros på Google Maps"
    ></iframe>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .venue {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    color: #2c2c2c;
  }

  .venue-name {
    font-family: 'Qwitcher Grypen', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd8d0;
  }

  .detail-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .detail-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    min-width: 5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .detail-value {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .venue-link {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #2c2c2c;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .getting-there-note {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #777;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    border-left: 2px solid #ddd8d0;
  }

  .getting-there-note a {
    color: #2c2c2c;
  }

  .map-frame {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd8d0;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
